      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON. ¶ J. E. Brown Esqr Inspector of forests of South Australia, Adelaide ¶ a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, esp...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.01.00c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-size: 10pt; ">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates, 1879.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">J. E. Brown Esqr Inspector of forests of South Australia, Adelaide</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg style="color: #ff0000; font-style: italic; "> </seg>
               <seg style="">forest-botany</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">being desirous of becoming a Fellow of the LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON, we, whose names are underwritten, beg leave to recommend him to that honour.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. Mueller, M.D. F.LS.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Form completed and signed by M; other supporters' autograph signatures. It is not known when M completed the form, nor when the other supporters signed it, but it must have been mailed by early 1879; the item is numbered accordingly.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">William Woolls Ph.D. F.LS</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Robt D Fitzgerald FLS</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">This recommendation must be signed by Three or more Fellows.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.B. – The Christian name of the Candidate must be stated at length, as well as his Residence, and any special qualifications he may possess.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society, on the</seg>
               <seg> </seg>3rd <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg>
               <seg> </seg>April 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">The Ballot will take place on the</seg>
               <seg> </seg>1st <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg>
               <seg> </seg>May 1879.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated bottom front: </seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Elected.</hi>
                     </seg> Rd.K.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">back, in ink</seg>: J. E. Brown, Esq | elected May 1 1879. </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">back, in pencil, in another hand</seg>: Adelaide, S.A.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
